el in\ntime, and which is consistent with the latest observational data of the CMB.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Dec 2013 14:43:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 May 2014 13:58:57 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 13 May 2014 06:56:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
